    "However, this proof theory could not be used to model and solve any of our three case studies.",
    "The reason is that the logic in question, LA r, is purely extensional, as admitted by the researchers in question:",
    "The logic presented in this study [LA r ] will be based on Classical Logic -henceforth CL.",
    "Moreover, all references to causality, laws of nature, and similar non-extensional concepts [such as belief, knowledge, and perception] will be out of the picture.",
